      "description": "An exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This S54-powered icon features a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically overhauled with documented rod bearing and VANOS service, the chassis has been meticulously preserved with zero subframe fatigue. The variable M differential lock provides optimal traction, while the factory suspension maintains its original geometric precision. Finished in flawless Laguna Seca Blue, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience with no deferred maintenance.",
